what this is all about?

1:16:03.726 --> 1:16:06.135
All the rebuilding
the house and the store, like--

1:16:06.287 --> 1:16:08.896
No, just, the family is
the most important thing to me.

1:16:09.123 --> 1:16:10.547
It's more important
than anything or anyone.

1:16:10.641 --> 1:16:12.900
I just want to get it right.

1:16:14.219 --> 1:16:15.886
Family first, right?

1:16:15.905 --> 1:16:17.238
Family first.

1:16:17.465 --> 1:16:19.799
Mommy!

1:16:19.817 --> 1:16:22.059
[laughter]

1:16:22.078 --> 1:16:23.911
Oh, my big girl!

1:16:25.489 --> 1:16:27.415
Look at her!

1:16:27.642 --> 1:16:29.083
-Y'all about the same size!
-I know.

1:16:30.086 --> 1:16:33.145
-Hey.
-Hey.

1:16:33.238 --> 1:16:34.905
You're ready
to go take this photo?

1:16:34.924 --> 1:16:37.574
Anthony, this is your family.

1:16:37.594 --> 1:16:39.409
