1:16:39.503 --> 1:16:41.670
Oh, of course you should.

1:16:41.823 --> 1:16:47.176
The plan was for me to come,
to stay a while, and to leave.

1:16:47.328 --> 1:16:50.179
I got this offer in toronto...

1:16:50.331 --> 1:16:52.164
So, you're leaving?

1:16:52.183 --> 1:16:55.759
The blueprints for
the redesign are complete,

1:16:55.778 --> 1:16:58.613
So, um,
technically my job's done.

1:17:00.007 --> 1:17:01.173
Unless--

1:17:01.266 --> 1:17:02.358
Yeah, your job here is done.

1:17:02.510 --> 1:17:06.345
I can oversee the build myself.

1:17:06.364 --> 1:17:08.956
My family's legacy, right?

1:17:09.108 --> 1:17:10.791
Yeah. It is.

1:17:14.964 --> 1:17:19.634
