1:17:19.785 --> 1:17:23.220
-Well, uh...
-Goodbye, anthony.

1:17:25.141 --> 1:17:29.310
♪♪

1:17:36.468 --> 1:17:38.819
[somber music playing]

1:17:41.399 --> 1:17:43.949
Anthony, you know, christmas
ain't until tomorrow, right?

1:17:46.070 --> 1:17:47.787
Someone dropped this off.

1:17:50.166 --> 1:17:51.332
It's nice.

1:17:51.483 --> 1:17:53.909
What happened, honey?

1:17:54.003 --> 1:17:56.562
I'm just ready to take
another crack at these pralines.

1:17:56.580 --> 1:17:59.748
You know, just because you don't
work in the shop with us

1:17:59.842 --> 1:18:02.659
Doesn't mean that you're not
a part of what we build.

1:18:02.753 --> 1:18:04.920
We all did this together.

1:18:05.072 --> 1:18:07.756
I know. I just...
I want to get this right.

1:18:07.909 --> 1:18:11.593
You know, and I don't know
what I'm missing.

1:18:11.746 --> 1:18:13.746
Don't lie to me now.

1:18:13.764 --> 1:18:16.357
You know exactly what
you're missing, don't you?

1:18:16.508 --> 1:18:19.251
Pralines aren't a metaphor,
grandma.

1:18:19.344 --> 1:18:21.845
Baby, let me say
something to you.

1:18:21.864 --> 1:18:24.699
Pralines are everything.

1:18:26.685 --> 1:18:28.761
You miss her, don't you?

1:18:28.779 --> 1:18:30.262
Yeah, but...

1:18:30.355 --> 1:18:32.522
And you want her back, right?

1:18:32.542 --> 1:18:35.434
You know, maybe
it's better this way.

1:18:35.453 --> 1:18:38.771
Maybe I'm supposed to buckle
down and get back to work

1:18:38.789 --> 1:18:41.941
And get back to my life
like it was before her.

1:18:42.034 --> 1:18:43.943
Is that what you really want?

1:18:43.961 --> 1:18:46.278
Hmm.

1:18:46.297 --> 1:18:50.966
Mmm. This looks pretty good.

1:18:51.060 --> 1:18:55.378
Mm, but you're right.
It's wrong, wrong, wrong.

1:18:55.473 --> 1:18:57.790
Not bad, just wrong.

1:18:57.808 --> 1:18:59.291
Ooh, and that's what happens

1:18:59.384 --> 1:19:01.627
When your recipe
isn't in balance.

1:19:01.645 --> 1:19:03.887
How much sugar is in that?

1:19:03.906 --> 1:19:06.966
A lot. Pralines are
all about sugar.

1:19:06.984 --> 1:19:09.818
Exactly. And your life
is all about work.

1:19:09.971 --> 1:19:11.912
But it isn't satisfying, is it?

1:19:12.064 --> 1:19:14.156
It's not even fun.

1:19:14.308 --> 1:19:16.399
Grandma.

1:19:16.419 --> 1:19:18.419
You want to know
what it is, anthony?

1:19:18.570 --> 1:19:20.570
My secret ingredient?

1:19:20.664 --> 1:19:23.165
I don't know, love?

1:19:23.259 --> 1:19:25.909
No, it's salt.

1:19:25.928 --> 1:19:27.762
Salt?

1:19:27.913 --> 1:19:30.155
Sometimes you just
need a little bit

1:19:30.249 --> 1:19:33.750
Of the unexpected
to make life sweeter,

1:19:33.770 --> 1:19:35.603
To bring everything
back into balance.

1:19:37.923 --> 1:19:40.274
Now, don't you want to make
life a little sweeter again?

1:19:46.616 --> 1:19:49.933
I tried,
but she won't answer my calls.

1:19:49.952 --> 1:19:51.844
Well, you have to try harder.

1:19:51.862 --> 1:19:53.454
It's that simple?

1:19:53.605 --> 1:19:55.456
Most things usually are.

1:19:57.126 --> 1:19:58.517
Thanks, grandma.

1:19:58.536 --> 1:20:00.352
You don't have to thank me.

1:20:00.371 --> 1:20:01.796
You just need to go
out and find that girl.

1:20:04.133 --> 1:20:08.469
Don't worry. I think
I might have an idea for that.

1:20:12.141 --> 1:20:14.809
♪♪

1:20:18.873 --> 1:20:21.206
