1:23:22.164 --> 1:23:25.390
Oh, I almost forgot. It's not
christmas without presents.

1:23:25.409 --> 1:23:27.650
Is this what I think it is?

1:23:27.670 --> 1:23:29.486
[laughs]

1:23:29.580 --> 1:23:32.172
[indistinct conversations]

1:23:34.677 --> 1:23:37.511
[gasps]

1:23:40.924 --> 1:23:44.760
Anthony, these are so good.

1:23:44.854 --> 1:23:46.669
-Yes.
-You did it!

1:23:46.764 --> 1:23:47.855
Chris: I can't believe it.

1:23:48.006 --> 1:23:50.415
-Mm!
-Yeah? Okay.

1:23:50.434 --> 1:23:53.176
-All right, one more thing.
-You're taking them?

1:23:53.195 --> 1:23:54.862
This is for you.

